src:
Hasil Pertandingan Barcelona vs Slavia Praha: Skor 0-0
06 Nov 2019, 02:55 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Barcelona hanya mampu bermain imbang ketika menjamu Slavia Praha dalam laga matchday keempat fase grup Liga Champions 2019-20 yang digelar di Camp Nou, Rabu (6/11/2019) dini hari WIB.
Gempuran yang dilakukan Lionel Messi cs tak mampu menghasilkan gol. Sebaliknya, Slavia sempat beberapa kali merepotkan lini pertahanan tuan rumah.
Berkat hasil ini, Barcelona masih bertengger di puncak klasemen Grup F dengan poin 8, sedangkan Slavia Praha masih terpuruk di dasar klasemen dengan perolehan dua poin.

Simak ulasan pertandingan selengkapnya di bawah ini.
text:
Match Results Barcelona vs Slavia Prague: Score 0-0
Nov 6 2019, 02:55 by Bola.net
Bola.net - Barcelona were only able to draw when entertaining Slavia Prague in the fourth matchday match of the Champions League group phase 2019-20 which was held at Camp Nou on Wednesday (11/06/2019) early morning hrs.
The onslaught by Lionel Messi cs could not produce a goal. Conversely, Slavia had several times to bother the host defense.
Thanks to these results, Barcelona still tops the Group F standings with 8 points, while Slavia Prague is still slumped at the bottom of the standings with two points.
